org.ica.utilityClasses

Class RenameContents

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.ica.utilityClasses.RenameContents

  • public class RenameContents
extends java.lang.Object
    This class contains only one public function execute(String oldName, CompositionBriques compositionBriques) which renames all the contents of a compositionBriques objects when it's name is changed.
    Author:
    Salim Ahmed
